headline: Lowe's Teams Up with NFL Superstars to Launch 'Earn Your Sunday,' Encouraging Fans to Get Projects Done Before Game Day
summary: Lowe's, the official home improvement partner of the NFL for the 7th consecutive year, today announced the launch of the Lowe's Earn Your Sunday campaign – a new call to motivate NFL fans to power through their home projects during the week, so Sundays can be reserved for football, family and relaxation without interruption.
